00:00:01,970 --> 00:00:02,980
Tsukiyama!

2
00:00:05,600 --> 00:00:07,980
It's been a while, Kirishima-san.

3
00:00:09,950 --> 00:00:10,990
What do you want?

4
00:00:11,410 --> 00:00:13,640
Friendly as always, I see.

5
00:00:14,220 --> 00:00:17,050
Though I suppose that's just part of your charm.

6
00:00:17,050 --> 00:00:19,530
You're sickening, you pig.

7
00:00:20,830 --> 00:00:22,500
The man with the eyepatch over there...

8
00:00:23,600 --> 00:00:24,700
You're new, right?

9
00:00:24,700 --> 00:00:25,880
U-Um...

10
00:00:25,880 --> 00:00:26,670
What's your name?

11
00:00:26,670 --> 00:00:28,000
K-Kaneki.

12
00:00:31,290 --> 00:00:32,880
What a marvelous aroma.

13
00:00:32,880 --> 00:00:34,490
Hey, you.

14
00:00:34,490 --> 00:00:37,870
You're being a nuisance, not to mention gross. 
Take a hike already.

15
00:00:37,870 --> 00:00:40,330
A bit harsh, aren't we?

16
00:00:41,000 --> 00:00:43,820
I'll be back some other time for a cup of coffee.

17
00:00:43,820 --> 00:00:45,480
Yoshimura should be around then.

18
00:00:45,890 --> 00:00:47,440
O-Okay...

19
00:00:47,440 --> 00:00:48,760
Charmed to meet you.

20
00:00:48,760 --> 00:00:50,360
Farewell, Kaneki-kun.

21
00:00:51,210 --> 00:00:52,320
Until we meet again...

22
00:00:54,290 --> 00:00:55,480
Who was that guy?

23
00:00:55,480 --> 00:00:56,830
You'd better keep an eye out for him.

24
00:00:57,480 --> 00:00:59,500
He's the scourge of the 20th Ward.

25
00:01:01,750 --> 00:01:05,430
And here we have a national specialty, the eyes of virgins.

26
00:01:05,430 --> 00:01:06,170
Thank you.

27
00:01:08,870 --> 00:01:10,590
Kaneki-kun, was it?

28
00:01:11,030 --> 00:01:12,330
How utterly captivating...

29
00:01:13,610 --> 00:01:14,970
that scent of his.

30
00:02:47,220 --> 00:02:48,260
What?

31
00:02:48,260 --> 00:02:50,060
Another jam bun today?

32
00:02:50,370 --> 00:02:53,380
It's fine. This is as good as cafeteria food gets.

33
00:02:53,380 --> 00:02:54,520
That's not good enough!

34
00:02:54,520 --> 00:02:56,060
You're still a growing girl, you know.

35
00:02:56,060 --> 00:02:59,400
Which one shall we choose?

36
00:02:59,400 --> 00:03:00,030
Fried chicken!

37
00:03:00,560 --> 00:03:01,710
Say "ahh!"

38
00:03:01,710 --> 00:03:02,990
Huh? It's fine.

39
00:03:03,540 --> 00:03:05,490
There's no way I'm gonna let you off with just bread.

40
00:03:05,490 --> 00:03:06,620
Now open up!

41
00:03:08,280 --> 00:03:09,270
Fine...

42
00:03:11,110 --> 00:03:12,880
I fiddled around a bit with the seasoning.

43
00:03:12,880 --> 00:03:13,820
What do you think?

44
00:03:15,960 --> 00:03:16,630
What is it?

45
00:03:17,380 --> 00:03:18,320
Ow!

46
00:03:19,000 --> 00:03:20,810
Well, it's pretty good.

47
00:03:20,810 --> 00:03:22,760
You're just saying that.

48
00:03:22,760 --> 00:03:24,170
No, I mean it.

49
